How to install KShowmail
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

Required packages:
------------------
- gcc
- KDE-Devel packages
- kdepimlibs and/or libkdepim
- kdepimlibs-devel and/or 

Installation:
-------------
tar xzf kshowmail-4.1.tar.gz
cd kshowmail-4.1
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kde4-config --prefix` .. <-- don't forget the ..!
make
make install (you have to be root)

to uninstall the project:
make uninstall (you have to be root)


